== 0.4.0 (2017-07-05)

* Cleanup error classes namespacing.

== 0.3.0 (2017-06-30)

* Rescue error conditions and re-raise them as HTTP::Client::Error sub-classes.

== 0.2.2 (2016-09-21)

* URI parser error for relative paths.

== 0.2.1 (2016-09-21)

* Module scoped errors.

== 0.2.0 (2016-06-10)

* Uncompress gzip and deflate responses.

== 0.1.2 (2016-06-09)

* Fix YARD documentation.
* Preserve headers in 301, 302 & 303 redirects.
* Handle 303, 307 & 308.

== 0.1.1 (2016-06-08)

* Less restrictive dependency versions.
* Fix body assignment in requests.
* Tests

== 0.1.0 (2016-06-08)

* Initial version.
